--- !u!114 &1096189509
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1096189507}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a12a7ee5defe9034d9ad56a40de26130, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  content: {fileID: 1573585148}
  backdrop: {fileID: 1845516912}
  backdropButton: {fileID: 1845516911}
  closeOnBackdrop: 0
  pausesGame: 1
  animDuration: 0.3
  backdropAlpha: 0.6
  titleText: {fileID: 1405061336}
  bodyText: {fileID: 1679640251}
  stepIndicatorText: {fileID: 137168992}
  nextButton: {fileID: 1207046408}
  nextButtonLabel: {fileID: 802552128}
  groups:
  - triggerLevel: 1
    doneKey: text_tutorial_done_1
    steps:
    - title: WELCOME!
      body: Welcome to Merge Mining! Each level has a fixed number of blocks you
        need to destroy.
    - title: BUY PICKAXES
      body: "Tap the SHOP button to buy a Lvl 1 pickaxe with your coins.\n\nEach
        level gives you a coin budget \u2014 spend it wisely!"
    - title: MERGE PICKAXES
      body: 'Drag a pickaxe onto another of the same level to merge into a stronger
        one.


        Higher level pickaxes deal much more damage!'
    - title: START THE BATTLE
      body: 'When you''re ready, tap the green START button.


        Your pickaxes
        will automatically attack the blocks above.'
    - title: WIN THE LEVEL
      body: 'Destroy all blocks to win!


        The more pickaxes you save, the
        more stars you get.


        Good luck!'
  - triggerLevel: 2
    doneKey: text_tutorial_done_2
    steps:
    - title: TIMER
      body: 'Each level has a time limit. If you run out, you lose!


        The
        timer is at the top-left during battle.'
    - title: FALLING BLOCKS
      body: "Blocks slowly descend toward your pickaxes.\n\nIf they reach the grid
        \u2014 you lose. Move fast!"
    - title: DURABILITY
      body: 'Each pickaxe has limited durability (green bar at the bottom).


        After
        many attacks, it breaks and disappears.'
    - title: BLOCK REGEN
      body: 'If you don''t damage a block for ~1.5 seconds, its HP regenerates!


        Focus
        your fire.'
    - title: SPECIAL BLOCKS
      body: 'Iron - only Lvl 3+ pickaxes can damage it

        Diamond - takes only
        50% damage

        Explosive - hurts pickaxes when broken

        Healer
        - heals nearby blocks

        Armored - reduces damage by 3

        Shell
        - regen after outer crack

        BOSS - destroys your weakest pickaxe every
        6s'
  - triggerLevel: 3
    doneKey: text_tutorial_done_3
    steps:
    - title: MODIFIERS
      body: 'Before each level you''ll choose 1 of 3 random modifiers.


        Each
        gives a bonus AND a drawback. Pick what fits your strategy!'
    - title: SACRIFICE
      body: "In battle, the pink SACRIFICE button on the right destroys your strongest
        pickaxe.\n\nIn exchange \u2014 every block on the field dies instantly!"
    - title: READY!
      body: You now know all the rules. Time to crush some blocks!
